K3s High Availability (HA) Installation Guide

Platform: Alpine Linux (OpenRC)
Mode: Embedded etcd
Topology: 3 Control Plane Nodes

1. Architecture Overview
1.1 Target Topology
Node	IP Address	Role
k3s-server-1	10.0.0.10	Control Plane + etcd
k3s-server-2	10.0.0.11	Control Plane + etcd
k3s-server-3	10.0.0.12	Control Plane + etcd

Optional:

Worker nodes

External Load Balancer (recommended for production)

2. System Requirements
2.1 Minimum Requirements (Per Control Plane Node)
2 vCPU
2 GB RAM (minimum)
20 GB disk
Static IP address
Time synchronization enabled
Required ports open

2.2 Required Open Ports
Port	Protocol	Purpose
6443	TCP	Kubernetes API
2379-2380	TCP	etcd
10250	TCP	kubelet
8472	UDP	Flannel VXLAN
